name: Kill Them Immediately
Lore: 'Darth Sidious instructed Nute Gunray to dispose of the Jedi ambassadors. Rune Haako was not so confident.',
Text: 'Use 5 Force to reveal opponent''s hand. If opponent has no duplicate cards there, place this Interrupt in Used Pile. OtherwiseUSED: place a revealed card in opponent''s Used Pile.LOST: all cards opponent has two or more of are lost. (Immune to Sense.)',
